      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "txt-title",
        "label": "'181 ALU MODULE v1 - Blinky family byte slice - solo Addy configuration",
        "position": {
          "x": -60,
          "y": -46
        },
        "rotation": 0,
        "layer": 0,
        "frequencyHz": null,
        "dutyCycle": null,
        "startHigh": null,
        "designator": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null,
        "filled": null,
        "fillColor": null,
        "borderColor": null,
        "startBit": null,
        "mirrored": null,
        "color": null,
        "fontSize": 6,
        "textColor": "Black"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "id": "txt-note",
        "label": "Layers 1-5 = optional population. RN1 = BKILL pulldowns (SIP9 bussed), RAEQ = A=B pull-up, RN2 = /FOE //SOE //AUXOE pull-ups (elements 5-9 NC), RSRIN = SRIN pulldown (LSR-safe idle). BKILL is ACTIVE-HIGH (high = U6 /OE deasserted, pulldowns give B=0). GND on pin 1 of H10/H11/H12/H14; data headers all-signal. Jumpers (pos 1-2 = solo/Addy): J1 LK_CN, J2 LK_ZC, J3 LK_BORROW. SRIN source host-strapped at H11.",
        "position": {
          "x": -60,
          "y": -38
        },
        "rotation": 0,
        "layer": 0,
        "frequencyHz": null,
        "dutyCycle": null,
        "startHigh": null,
        "designator": null,
        "width": null,
        "height": null,
        "filled": null,
        "fillColor": null,
        "borderColor": null,
        "startBit": null,
        "mirrored": null,
        "color": null,
        "fontSize": 3,
        "textColor": "Grey"
      },
